query:
SELECT t.id as "id!: Uuid",
                      t.name,
                      t.slug,
                      t.identifier,
                      t.icon,
                      t.color,
                      t.document_storage_path,
                      t.created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                      t.updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
               FROM teams t
               INNER JOIN team_projects tp ON t.id = tp.team_id
               WHERE tp.project_id = $1
               ORDER BY t.name ASC
